## Automatic Memory System

This project uses **DMM** with automatic MCP integration. You have access to
memory tools that work transparently in the background.

### MCP Tools Available

| Tool | Purpose | When to Use |
|------|---------|-------------|
| `dmm_query` | Get relevant context | Start of every task |
| `dmm_remember` | Save learnings | After important decisions |
| `dmm_forget` | Deprecate outdated info | When info becomes obsolete |
| `dmm_status` | System health | If something seems wrong |
| `dmm_conflicts` | Find contradictions | Periodically or when confused |

